Package zserio.runtime.validation

This package contains classes needed for validation code generated by Zserio.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ValidationBitStreamReader
    The bit stream reader used in validate() method generated by Zserio.
    ValidationError
    Describes validation error which is reported from validation code generated by Zserio.
    ValidationReport
    Defines validation report which is returned from validation code generated by Zserio.
    ValidationSqliteUtil
    Contains SQL utilities need for validation code generated by Zserio.
    ValidationSqliteUtil.ColumnDescription
    Describes the table column.
    ValidationTimer
    Validation timer used from validation code generated by Zserio.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ValidationError.Type
    Defines type of validation error.
